Ford Motor Company\">F</a></span>)</strong> fell after the company posted its 3Q24 financial report that featured a downward revision to its FY24E adjusted EBIT to reflect supplier disruptions at its Ford Pro segment. The company\u2019s Model e division is still a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152533018/image_2152533018.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743673-finding-some-value-in-ford", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 23:06:48"}, {"id": "4743672", "title": "Panasonic: AI And HVAC Businesses Have Favorable Prospects (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784615/image_1325784615.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Panasonic headquarters in Silicon Valley\" data-id=\"1325784615\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784615/image_1325784615.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784615/image_1325784615.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784615/image_1325784615.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784615/image_1325784615.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784615/image_1325784615.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784615/image_1325784615.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784615/image_1325784615.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784615/image_1325784615.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\"